{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1889,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":7852,"text":"[\"Oedipus Rex\"]"},{"time":15397,"text":"[\"The Lion King\"]"},{"time":22485,"text":"[\"Titus\"]"},{"time":37727,"text":"[\"Frida\"]"},{"time":53751,"text":"[\"The Magic Flute\"]"},{"time":60197,"text":"[\"Across The Universe\"]"},{"time":75710,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":80262,"text":"Julie Taymor: Thank you.\nThank you very much."},{"time":82469,"text":"That's a few samples of the theater, opera"},{"time":85186,"text":"and films that I have done\nover the last 20 years."},{"time":88528,"text":"But what I'd like to begin with right now"},{"time":90566,"text":"is to take you back to a moment"},{"time":92469,"text":"that I went through in Indonesia,"},{"time":94934,"text":"which is a seminal moment in my life"},{"time":97071,"text":"and, like all myths,"},{"time":99151,"text":"these stories need to be retold"},{"time":101406,"text":"and told, lest we forget them."},{"time":103905,"text":"And when I'm in the turbulent\ntimes, as we know,"},{"time":106929,"text":"that I am right now, through the crucible"},{"time":109317,"text":"and the fire of transformation,"},{"time":111508,"text":"which is what all of you do, actually."},{"time":114126,"text":"Anybody who creates knows\nthere's that point where"},{"time":117250,"text":"it hasn't quite become\nthe phoenix or the burnt char."},{"time":122359,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":124457,"text":"And I am right there on the edge,"},{"time":127362,"text":"which I'll tell you about, another story."},{"time":129339,"text":"I want to go back to Indonesia"},{"time":130792,"text":"where I was about 21, 22\nyears, a long time ago,"},{"time":134476,"text":"on a fellowship."},{"time":135700,"text":"And I found myself, after two years there"},{"time":138630,"text":"and performing and learning,\non the island of Bali,"},{"time":141979,"text":"on the edge of a crater, Gunung Batur."},{"time":145806,"text":"And I was in a village where there was"},{"time":148823,"text":"an initiation ceremony for the young men,"},{"time":151615,"text":"a rite of passage."},{"time":153179,"text":"Little did I know that it\nwas mine as well."},{"time":155731,"text":"And as I sat in this temple square"},{"time":158190,"text":"under this gigantic beringin banyan tree,"},{"time":161190,"text":"in the dark, there was no\nelectricity, just the full moon,"},{"time":166027,"text":"down in this empty square,"},{"time":168083,"text":"and I heard the most beautiful sounds,"},{"time":170233,"text":"like a Charles Ives concert"},{"time":172064,"text":"as I listened to the gamelan music"},{"time":174107,"text":"from all the different villagers that came"},{"time":176156,"text":"for this once-every-five-years ceremony."},{"time":179554,"text":"And I thought I was alone\nin the dark under this tree."},{"time":183149,"text":"And all of a sudden, out of the dark,"},{"time":185980,"text":"from the other end of the square,"},{"time":187864,"text":"I saw the glint of mirrors\nlit by the moon."},{"time":191772,"text":"And these 20 old men who I'd seen before"},{"time":195331,"text":"all of a sudden stood up in these\nfull warrior costumes"},{"time":200633,"text":"with the headdress and the spears,"},{"time":203118,"text":"and no one was in the square,\nand I was hidden in the shadows."},{"time":207480,"text":"No one was there, and they came out,"},{"time":209841,"text":"and they did this incredible dance."},{"time":213480,"text":"\"Huhuhuhuhuhuhuhahahahaha.\""},{"time":217172,"text":"And they moved their bodies\nand they came forward,"},{"time":220345,"text":"and the lights bounced off these costumes."},{"time":223147,"text":"And I've been in theater\nsince I was 11 years old,"},{"time":226563,"text":"and performing, creating, and I went,"},{"time":229777,"text":"\"Who are they performing for"},{"time":231920,"text":"with these elaborate costumes,"},{"time":234267,"text":"these extraordinary headdresses?\""},{"time":236294,"text":"And I realized that they were\nperforming for God,"},{"time":241081,"text":"whatever that means."},{"time":243792,"text":"But somehow, it didn't\nmatter about the publicity."},{"time":247380,"text":"There was no money involved."},{"time":249631,"text":"It wasn't going to be written down.\nIt was no news."},{"time":252851,"text":"And there were these incredible artists"},{"time":254997,"text":"that felt for me like an eternity\nas they performed."},{"time":258498,"text":"The next moment,"},{"time":260583,"text":"as soon as they finished\nand disappeared into the shadows,"},{"time":264643,"text":"a young man with a propane\nlantern came on,"},{"time":267149,"text":"hung it up on a tree, set up a curtain."},{"time":269400,"text":"The village square was filled\nwith hundreds of people."},{"time":272861,"text":"And they put on an opera all night long."},{"time":275399,"text":"Human beings needed the light."},{"time":277659,"text":"They needed the light to see."},{"time":280296,"text":"So what I gained and gathered\nfrom this incredible,"},{"time":283944,"text":"seminal moment in my life\nas a young artist"},{"time":286556,"text":"was that you must be true"},{"time":289879,"text":"to what you believe as an artist\nall the way through,"},{"time":293951,"text":"but you also have to be aware"},{"time":297490,"text":"that the audience is out there\nin our lives at this time,"},{"time":300979,"text":"and they also need the light."},{"time":302384,"text":"And it's this incredible balance"},{"time":304547,"text":"that I think that we walk"},{"time":306296,"text":"when we are creating something\nthat is breaking ground,"},{"time":309629,"text":"that's trying to do something\nyou've never seen before,"},{"time":312283,"text":"that imaginary world"},{"time":313969,"text":"where you actually don't know\nwhere you're going to end up,"},{"time":317346,"text":"that's the fine line\non the edge of a crater"},{"time":320112,"text":"that I have walked my whole life."},{"time":322742,"text":"What I would like to do now is to tell you"},{"time":325290,"text":"a little bit"},{"time":327096,"text":"about how I work.\nLet's take \"The Lion King.\""},{"time":329953,"text":"You saw many examples of my work up there,"},{"time":332205,"text":"but it's one that people know."},{"time":334150,"text":"I start with the notion of the ideograph."},{"time":336849,"text":"An ideograph is like a brush\npainting, a Japanese brush painting."},{"time":340224,"text":"Three strokes, you get\nthe whole bamboo forest."},{"time":343733,"text":"I go to the concept of \"The Lion King\""},{"time":346264,"text":"and I say, \"What is the essence of it?"},{"time":348332,"text":"What is the abstraction?"},{"time":349968,"text":"If I were to reduce this entire story"},{"time":353229,"text":"into one image, what would it be?\""},{"time":355970,"text":"The circle. The circle. It's so obvious."},{"time":358924,"text":"The circle of life. The\ncircle of Mufasa's mask."},{"time":362901,"text":"The circle that, when we come\nto Act II and there's a drought,"},{"time":367441,"text":"how do you express drought?"},{"time":368920,"text":"It's a circle of silk on the floor"},{"time":372079,"text":"that disappears into the hole\nin the stage floor."},{"time":376133,"text":"The circle of life comes in the wheels"},{"time":378762,"text":"of the gazelles that leap."},{"time":381210,"text":"And you see the mechanics."},{"time":382932,"text":"And being a theater person, what I know\nand love about the theater"},{"time":386310,"text":"is that when the audience comes in"},{"time":388005,"text":"and they suspend their disbelief,"},{"time":389799,"text":"when you see men walking or women walking"},{"time":392634,"text":"with a platter of grass on their heads,"},{"time":394531,"text":"you know it's the savanna."},{"time":396147,"text":"You don't question that."},{"time":397691,"text":"I love the apparent truth of theater."},{"time":400175,"text":"I love that people are willing\nto fill in the blanks."},{"time":403772,"text":"The audience is willing to say,"},{"time":405792,"text":"\"Oh, I know that's not a real sun."},{"time":408792,"text":"You took pieces of sticks."},{"time":411100,"text":"You added silk to the bottom."},{"time":413195,"text":"You suspended these pieces. You\nlet it fall flat on the floor."},{"time":416899,"text":"And as it rises with the strings,\nI see that it's a sun."},{"time":421302,"text":"But the beauty of it\nis that it's just silk and sticks."},{"time":425709,"text":"And in a way, that is what makes\nit spiritual."},{"time":430261,"text":"That's what moves you."},{"time":431706,"text":"It's not the actual literal\nsunrise that's coming."},{"time":435922,"text":"It's the art of it."},{"time":437453,"text":"So in the theater, as much\nas the story is critical"},{"time":442813,"text":"and the book and the language,"},{"time":444718,"text":"the telling of the story, how it's told,"},{"time":449369,"text":"the mechanics, the methods that you use,"},{"time":452987,"text":"is equal to the story itself."},{"time":455586,"text":"And I'm one who loves\nhigh tech and low tech."},{"time":458924,"text":"So I could go from --"},{"time":460723,"text":"For instance, I'll show you\nsome \"Spider-Man\" later,"},{"time":463224,"text":"these incredible machines\nthat move people along."},{"time":465800,"text":"But the fact is, without the dancer"},{"time":468166,"text":"who knows how to use his body\nand swing on those wires,"},{"time":470919,"text":"it's nothing."},{"time":472706,"text":"So now I'm going to show you"},{"time":475615,"text":"some clips from the other big\nproject of my life this year,"},{"time":479933,"text":"\"The Tempest.\""},{"time":480975,"text":"It's a movie. I did \"The\nTempest\" on a stage three times"},{"time":485068,"text":"in the theater since 1984, '86,"},{"time":488305,"text":"and I love the play."},{"time":490509,"text":"I did it always with a male Prospero."},{"time":493035,"text":"And all of a sudden, I thought,"},{"time":494697,"text":"\"Well, who am I gonna\nget to play Prospero?"},{"time":496783,"text":"Why not Helen Mirren?\nShe's a great actor. Why not?\""},{"time":500505,"text":"And this material really did work\nfor a woman equally as well."},{"time":503765,"text":"So now, let's take a look\nat some of the images"},{"time":506860,"text":"from \"The Tempest.\""},{"time":508853,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":525220,"text":"(Video) Prospera: Hast thou, spirit, performed\nto the point the tempest that I bade thee?"},{"time":529483,"text":"Ariel: I boarded the king's ship.\nIn every cabin, I flamed amazement."},{"time":537664,"text":"Prospera: At first sight,\nthey have changed eyes."},{"time":540620,"text":"Miranda: Do you love me?"},{"time":541815,"text":"Ferdinand: Beyond all limit."},{"time":543191,"text":"HM: They are both in either's powers."},{"time":545783,"text":"Trinculo: Misery acquaints\na man with strange bedfellows."},{"time":550914,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":554156,"text":"Looking for business, governor?"},{"time":557633,"text":"Caliban: Hast thou not\ndropped from heaven?"},{"time":559705,"text":"Stephano: Out of the moon,\nI do assure thee."},{"time":562190,"text":"Prospera: Caliban!"},{"time":564187,"text":"Caliban: This island is mine."},{"time":566452,"text":"Prospera: For this, be sure,\ntonight thou shalt have cramps."},{"time":569997,"text":"Antonio: Here lies your brother no\nbetter than the earth he lies upon."},{"time":573506,"text":"Sebastian: Draw thy sword."},{"time":575305,"text":"And I, the king, shall love thee."},{"time":578914,"text":"Prospera: I will plague\nthem all, even to roaring."},{"time":586133,"text":"Ariel: I have made you mad."},{"time":596874,"text":"Prospera: We are such stuff\nas dreams are made on."},{"time":599919,"text":"and our little life\nis rounded with a sleep."},{"time":604130,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":609455,"text":"JT: Okay."},{"time":612305,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":616279,"text":"So I went from theater,\ndoing \"The Tempest\""},{"time":618707,"text":"on the stage in a very\nlow-budget production"},{"time":621031,"text":"many years ago,"},{"time":622669,"text":"and I love the play, and I also think"},{"time":625114,"text":"it's Shakespeare's last play,"},{"time":627138,"text":"and it really lends itself,\nas you can see, to cinema."},{"time":630818,"text":"But I'm just going to give\nyou a little example about"},{"time":633366,"text":"how one stages it in theater"},{"time":635271,"text":"and then how one takes\nthat same idea or story"},{"time":639332,"text":"and moves it into cinema."},{"time":642324,"text":"The ideograph that I talked\nto you about before,"},{"time":645420,"text":"what is it for \"The Tempest\"?"},{"time":647531,"text":"What, if I were to boil it down,"},{"time":650357,"text":"would be the one image that I could"},{"time":652670,"text":"hang my hat on for this?"},{"time":654917,"text":"And it was the sand castle,"},{"time":657205,"text":"the idea of nurture versus nature,"},{"time":660345,"text":"that we build these civilizations --"},{"time":662800,"text":"she speaks about it at the end,\nHelen Mirren's Prospera --"},{"time":665755,"text":"we build them, but under nature,\nunder the grand tempest,"},{"time":671228,"text":"these cloud-capped towers, these\ngorgeous palaces will fade"},{"time":676723,"text":"and there will -- leave not a rack behind."},{"time":680946,"text":"So in the theater, I started the play,"},{"time":683575,"text":"it was a black sand rake, white cyc,"},{"time":686637,"text":"and there was a little girl,\nMiranda, on the horizon,"},{"time":689562,"text":"building a drip castle, a sand castle."},{"time":692230,"text":"And as she was there\non the edge of that stage,"},{"time":695670,"text":"two stagehands all in black"},{"time":699031,"text":"with watering cans ran along the top"},{"time":703535,"text":"and started to pour water\non the sand castle,"},{"time":708162,"text":"and the sand castle\nstarted to drip and sink,"},{"time":710932,"text":"but before it did,"},{"time":712331,"text":"the audience saw\nthe black-clad stagehands."},{"time":716571,"text":"The medium was apparent. It was banal.\nWe saw it."},{"time":721158,"text":"But as they started to pour the water,"},{"time":724141,"text":"the light changed from showing\nyou the black-clad stagehands"},{"time":727873,"text":"to focusing, this rough magic\nthat we do in theater,"},{"time":731187,"text":"it focused right on the water itself."},{"time":734740,"text":"And all of a sudden,\nthe audience's perspective changes."},{"time":738962,"text":"It becomes something magically large."},{"time":742468,"text":"It becomes the rainstorm."},{"time":745100,"text":"The masked actors,\nthe puppeteers, they disappear,"},{"time":748744,"text":"and the audience makes\nthat leap into this world,"},{"time":751944,"text":"into this imaginary world of \"The\nTempest\" actually happening."},{"time":756267,"text":"Now the difference"},{"time":757696,"text":"when I went and did it in the cinema,"},{"time":760299,"text":"I started the actual movie"},{"time":762683,"text":"with a close-up of a sand\ncastle, a black sand castle,"},{"time":767965,"text":"and what cinema can do is,"},{"time":769803,"text":"by using camera, perspective,"},{"time":773259,"text":"and also long shots and close-ups,"},{"time":776001,"text":"it started on a close-up\nof the sand castle,"},{"time":778320,"text":"and as it pulled away,"},{"time":780203,"text":"you saw that it was a miniature\nsitting in the palm"},{"time":783237,"text":"of the girl's hands."},{"time":785140,"text":"And so I could play with the medium,"},{"time":786968,"text":"and why I move from one medium to another"},{"time":789920,"text":"is to be able to do this."},{"time":791403,"text":"Now I'm going to take you to \"Spider-Man.\""},{"time":793834,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":824794,"text":"(Video) Peter Parker: ♪\nStanding on the precipice,"},{"time":827621,"text":"I can soar away from this. ♪"},{"time":832100,"text":"JT: We're trying to do\neverything in live theater"},{"time":834458,"text":"that you can't do in two dimensions"},{"time":836377,"text":"in film and television."},{"time":838903,"text":"PP: ♪ Rise above yourself\nand take control. ♪"},{"time":842833,"text":"George Tsypin: We're looking at New\nYork from a Spider-Man point of view."},{"time":846334,"text":"Spider Man is not bound by gravity."},{"time":848479,"text":"Manhattan in the show is not\nbound by gravity either."},{"time":851637,"text":"PP: ♪ Be yourself and rise above it all. ♪"},{"time":855856,"text":"Ensemble: ♪ Sock! Pow! ♪"},{"time":859959,"text":"♪ Slam! Scratch! ♪"},{"time":862544,"text":"Danny Ezralow: I don't want you\nto even think there's a choreographer."},{"time":864745,"text":"It's real, what's happening."},{"time":865871,"text":"I prefer you to see people moving,"},{"time":868744,"text":"and you're going, \"Whoa, what was that?\""},{"time":870930,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":883151,"text":"JT: If I give enough movement\nin the sculpture,"},{"time":885414,"text":"and the actor moves their head,\nyou feel like it's alive."},{"time":888426,"text":"It's really comic book live.\nIt's a comic book coming alive."},{"time":891376,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":898577,"text":"Bono: They're mythologies."},{"time":899739,"text":"They're modern myths,\nthese comic book heroes."},{"time":903365,"text":"PP: ♪ They believe. ♪"},{"time":909328,"text":"(Screams)"},{"time":913005,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":930766,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":933034,"text":"JT: Ohhhh. What was that?"},{"time":937644,"text":"Circus, rock 'n' roll, drama."},{"time":939915,"text":"What the hell are we doing\nup there on that stage?"},{"time":942757,"text":"Well, one last story, very quickly."},{"time":945419,"text":"After I was in that village,\nI crossed the lake,"},{"time":948289,"text":"and I saw that the volcano was erupting"},{"time":951378,"text":"on the other side, Gunung Batur,"},{"time":953131,"text":"and there was a dead volcano\nnext to the live volcano."},{"time":956216,"text":"I didn't think I'd be\nswallowed by the volcano,"},{"time":958479,"text":"and I am here."},{"time":959823,"text":"But it's very easy to climb up, is it not?"},{"time":963760,"text":"You hold on to the roots,"},{"time":965345,"text":"you put your foot in the little rocks"},{"time":968545,"text":"and climb up there,\nand you get to the top,"},{"time":971127,"text":"and I was with a good\nfriend who was an actor,"},{"time":973417,"text":"and we said, \"Let's go up there."},{"time":975437,"text":"Let's see if we can come close to the edge"},{"time":977485,"text":"of that live volcano.\""},{"time":979621,"text":"And we climbed up and we got\nto the very top,"},{"time":982473,"text":"and we're on the edge, on this precipice,"},{"time":984978,"text":"Roland disappears into the sulfur smoke"},{"time":987391,"text":"at the volcano at the other end,"},{"time":989328,"text":"and I'm up there alone"},{"time":991170,"text":"on this incredible precipice."},{"time":993906,"text":"Did you hear the lyrics?"},{"time":995527,"text":"I'm on the precipice looking down"},{"time":997853,"text":"into a dead volcano to my left."},{"time":1000164,"text":"To my right is sheer shale.\nIt's coming off."},{"time":1003992,"text":"I'm in thongs and sarongs.\nIt was many years ago."},{"time":1007760,"text":"And no hiking boots."},{"time":1009385,"text":"And he's disappeared, this\nmad French gypsy actor,"},{"time":1013344,"text":"off in the smoke, and I realize,"},{"time":1016648,"text":"I can't go back the way that I've come.\nI can't."},{"time":1020576,"text":"So I throw away my camera.\nI throw away my thongs,"},{"time":1025257,"text":"and I looked at the line\nstraight in front of me,"},{"time":1028486,"text":"and I got down on all fours like a cat,"},{"time":1032119,"text":"and I held with my knees to either side"},{"time":1035142,"text":"of this line in front of me,"},{"time":1037535,"text":"for 30 yards or 30 feet, I don't know."},{"time":1040577,"text":"The wind was massively blowing,"},{"time":1043290,"text":"and the only way I could\nget to the other side"},{"time":1046720,"text":"was to look at the line\nstraight in front of me."},{"time":1049163,"text":"I know you've all been there."},{"time":1051166,"text":"I'm in the crucible right now."},{"time":1053139,"text":"It's my trial by fire."},{"time":1055003,"text":"It's my company's trials by fire."},{"time":1057333,"text":"We survive because our theme\nsong is \"Rise Above.\""},{"time":1061590,"text":"Boy falls from the sky, rise above."},{"time":1064731,"text":"It's right there in the palm\nof both of our hands,"},{"time":1067145,"text":"of all of my company's hands."},{"time":1068772,"text":"I have beautiful collaborators,\nand we as creators"},{"time":1072340,"text":"only get there all together."},{"time":1074351,"text":"I know you understand that."},{"time":1076540,"text":"And you just stay going forward,"},{"time":1078965,"text":"and then you see this extraordinary thing"},{"time":1081606,"text":"in front of your eyes."},{"time":1083152,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1084452,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}